videos.description: Lagerald Vick drives down the lane and throws down the thunderous one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Kansas' Vick soars for the dunk

videos.description: Ernie Duncan knocks down a three followed by an Azubuike dunk then Ernie Duncan comes back again and drains a three.
videos.headline: Vermont and Kansas trade buckets early in first

videos.description: Kansas' Lagerald Vick is hitting threes from all over the court including this one over a Vermont player's outstretched arm.
videos.headline: Vick can't miss from 3
